response.original_title: Yoga Link: Shoulder Shape-Up with Jill Miller
response.overview: Join acclaimed yoga teacher Jill Miller for Yoga Link | Shoulder Shape-Up, a unique Yoga-based practice specifically designed to break through the weakness and congestion in your shoulders caused by the unhealthy habits of our modern lifestyles. Unlock the mobility of your shoulders and arms and reconnect to the national dexterity buried within.
response.tagline: Create Dynamic Freedom in Your Shoulders
